    body: `⚙ ${$json.routineName} routine fired.\n\nSession: ${$json.claude_code_session_url || 'pending'}\nSession ID: ${$json.claude_code_session_id || 'pending'}\n\n(Langfuse trace URL will be posted by the routine itself on completion.)`
